{"tid":450594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有直播] 港超聯 28/10 - 20:00 - 陽光元朗 vs R&F富力","createTime":"2017-10-28T10:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T07:54:05.000Z","uid":66314,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ca2da44f407e951fd1a034647107daaa5a4d4e","tid":450594,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"直播Link：<br />\n手機版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/mlive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fmlive%2F&d=KCsqmQiBR0D6uDrfmw%2Fqxsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b76116d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/mlive/</a>　　　　　　　　　　 　<br />\n網頁版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Flive%2F&d=KCsqmQiBR0D6uDrfmw%2Fqxsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1e7cf31b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/live/</a><br />\n<br />\n場地: 元朗大球場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171027/photo/bkn-20171027232654975-1027_00882_001_01b.jpg?20171027232708\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171027%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171027232654975-1027_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20171027232708&h=f856373a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8c128c081eb3596e86c89121bce0fb64b770bdb","tid":450594,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"兩軍情報：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">陽光元朗</span><br />\n上周在高級組銀牌賽8強賽事，戰至加時階段以4比2擊敗和富大埔的陽光元朗，恰巧跟R&amp;F富力於菁英盃的首輪分組賽輪空，令兩隊原定於8月尾上演的聯賽得以安排補賽。元朗主教練曾昭達表示，勝仗令球隊士氣大振：「球員好落力，我非常欣賞佢哋喺場上嘅拚搏精神。我承認我哋係幸運嘅一方，始終雙方埋門都多，只係我哋把握得比人哋好，不過整體而言，球員發揮得幾好。贏波對球隊上下嘅信心都有所提升，球隊嘅目標都係向盃賽進發，尤其係之前有幾場都係喺優勢之下輸波，所以呢場波算係一支強心針。」<br />\n<br />\n「達Sir」坦言對富力的認知不多，惟有向凍結對手主力着手：「對手實力強，其中如般連奴亦係個人能力強嘅球員，希望可以盡量喺部署上做多啲，因為始終富力近3個星期都冇喺港超亮相，所以佢哋仍然存在好多未知數。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力</span><br />\nR&amp;F富力今季分別因颱風及主場問題，有多達3場聯賽均要延期，球隊上場出戰本地賽事已經是1個多月前於高級組銀牌賽首圈的賽事，最終以1比2不敵理文出局。主教練馬里科透露，他在休戰期間曾為球隊安排友賽，讓球員保持比賽狀態，同時亦強調球隊會保持自己的足球風格：「我哋會堅持自己嘅足球風格，並為首場勝利而戰。球隊喺近3星期合共踢咗3場友賽並且贏波，球員喺操練期間亦表現得好好，佢哋所需要做嘅，就係要對自己更有信心。」"},{"pid":"76dd7f9af0caa5a338bd74eb1d28aab62fb2afff","tid":450594,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"港超積分榜<br />\n1\t傑志\t4賽10分 +9<br />\n2\t飛馬\t4賽10分 +3<br />\n3\t南區\t5賽9分 +3<br />\n4\t大埔 5賽8分 +4<br />\n5\t夢想FC 4賽7分 -3<br />\n6\t<span style=\"color: orange;\">元朗\t4賽6分 -3</span><br />\n7\t理文\t3賽4分 0<br />\n8\t<span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力 2賽0分 -3</span><br />\n9\t東方龍獅\t4賽0分 -5<br />\n10\t流浪 3賽0分 -1"},{"pid":"16a9f04326bb382d63f1fbfef37f15db70fa6952","tid":450594,"uid":66314,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">元朗</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">R&amp;F富力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nlike呢個留言 = 支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩隊欖炒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c921fc2802c6815d40a1cca621e536fb2fb133dc","tid":450594,"uid":33053,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"畜力全隊食撚屎"},{"pid":"7e861ffbf3cb229aaa688b04fc30f9c1b95d7d29","tid":450594,"uid":68796,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"rubbish ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e35b087a750c5d551c2870faddc088bdb2461b4","tid":450594,"uid":44457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>rub